---
title: Activity Diagram - Pengelolaan Housekeeping
---
flowchart TD
    Start([Pagi Hari / Setelah Check-out]) --> Trigger{Trigger<br/>Pembuatan Task}
    Trigger -->|Check-out| TaskCO[INSERT task type='checkout-cleaning']
    Trigger -->|Cron Daily 06:00| TaskDaily[INSERT task type='daily' untuk semua occupied]
    TaskCO --> Listed
    TaskDaily --> Listed[Task Muncul di /rooms HK Filter]
    Listed --> HKBuka[Petugas Buka Aplikasi]
    HKBuka --> AsignedTask{Task<br/>Ter-assign?}
    AsignedTask -->|Tidak| Assign[Manager Assign ke Petugas]
    Assign --> HKBuka
    AsignedTask -->|Ya| Start1[Klik 'Mulai']
    Start1 --> UpdateProgress[UPDATE status='in_progress']
    UpdateProgress --> DoCleaning[Lakukan Pembersihan]
    DoCleaning --> Check{Cek<br/>Standar?}
    Check -->|Belum OK| DoCleaning
    Check -->|OK| Photo[Foto Bukti]
    Photo --> Submit[Klik 'Selesai']
    Submit --> UpdateDone[UPDATE status='completed']
    UpdateDone --> UpdateRoom[UPDATE rooms status='available']
    UpdateRoom --> Notif[Toast 'Kamar Siap']
    Notif --> End([Kamar Siap Dijual Kembali])

    classDef startEnd fill:#c8e6c9,stroke:#2e7d32,color:#000
    classDef decision fill:#fff9c4,stroke:#f57f17,color:#000
    classDef action fill:#bbdefb,stroke:#1565c0,color:#000
    class Start,End startEnd
    class Trigger,AsignedTask,Check decision
    class TaskCO,TaskDaily,Listed,HKBuka,Assign,Start1,UpdateProgress,DoCleaning,Photo,Submit,UpdateDone,UpdateRoom,Notif action
